3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with network structures and their characteristics, which can be related to systems and control. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the slow mixing problem in random walk-based sampling methods, which is a common problem in data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with network structures and their characteristics, which can be related to networking and internet architecture.
